    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption Friday with a front-page article about fear among Pakistanis in Lodi, Calif., after the arrest last year of two local men on terrorism charges misstated the name of a boy pictured with Raheela Hayat, whose brother, Hamid Hayat, was found guilty in the case. He is Jalal Hashim Usman, not Hamid. In some copies, the caption misstated the boy's relationship to Hamid Hayat. He is his nephew, not his son.</p>
      </block>
